"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"[跳至内容](#content)\\n\\n## [贰佰圆](http://www.stevenwu.me/ \\\"贰佰圆\\\")\\n\\n## 每年域名续费一百元，空间续租一百元。\\n\\n<!-- .site-branding -->\\n\\n*   [INTEGRITY AND COMPLIANCE](http://www.stevenwu.me/integrity-and-compliance)\\n*   [PRESS ROOM](http://www.stevenwu.me/press-room)\\n*   [INVESTOR RELATIONS](http://www.stevenwu.me/investor-relations)\\n*   [CONTACT US](http://www.stevenwu.me/contact-us)\\n\\n<!-- #masthead -->\\n\\n## 不做屏幕的奴隶\\n\\n<!-- .entry-header -->\\n\\n这两天老是觉得两眼昏花，脑袋空空，十分无力。仔细一想，最近两眼一直盯着屏幕，不晕才怪。为了避免这种状态再次出现，列下四条训诫，督促自己。\\n\\n1\\\\. Google Reader上有营养的Feeds push到Kindle上看，其他蛋疼类Feeds周末在电脑上扫一次即可。\\n\\n2\\\\. Kindle上被推送来的Feeds，阅读时注意筛选，泛读即可，避免资讯的疲劳轰炸。重要的文章可以先Mark之，日后再做精读。\\n\\n3.Kindle上的书籍分两种，打发时间类的书应该在琐碎时间阅读，比如上下班。严肃类书籍应该在整块时间阅读，比如睡前。\\n\\n4\\\\. SNS/微博这类扁平类社交工具，尽量少用，慎言。\\n\\n珍惜生命，原理网络。\\n\\n<!-- .entry-footer -->\\n\\n<!-- #post-142 -->\\n\\n## 文章导航\\n\\n### 没有评论\\n\\n<!-- #main -->\\n\\n<!-- #content -->\\n\\n<!-- #colophon -->\\n\",\"timestamp\":1639497540,\"title\":\"不做屏幕的奴隶\"},\"digest\":\"W-NDxWAAgKqhFIOvNOAu4n4OnBLDqh5C_hhhoSxmoLk\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x298C3Cb3E6b3EA2d9DA7f51768dad0849A26eF64\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"-VNS4I-oysNEYEHe7UY9kdsPWtT6_nJ-XHyhd3zle3Y\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"gjJRYU2nCAAHd4461UDqcfgAMBSUzYjeyj0_8ZbeeQU\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"BuNGkb5bG05mrJ4TCQINoM9sOAGw3vBp2roem0S4swzlVensPaGwOFdw4iATcnMMjtS2MFli3HJii8Sk4NppkA\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x1980362aaa5e5ce0033c7f7787646c48a9dbc4c9cb90844cfa84da508d8cb2a82ef38176d6238bcc11a92aa2ac6b9924822ce67c0d609c85163b3574c8ea1b061c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"-VNS4I-oysNEYEHe7UY9kdsPWtT6_nJ-XHyhd3zle3Y\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"gjJRYU2nCAAHd4461UDqcfgAMBSUzYjeyj0_8ZbeeQU\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"W-NDxWAAgKqhFIOvNOAu4n4OnBLDqh5C_hhhoSxmoLk\"}"